item.title: Highlights of Python 3.3
item.description:
Description

This will be a review session, covering some of the interesting features in Python 3.3. For the benefit of attendees that are still primarily using Python 2.x, the presentation will also cover a few of the key advantages of the Python 3.x series that aren't available in Python 2.7 or as backports on the Python Package Index.
item.dc:creator: Nick Coghlan
